==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Monotonical
<hw>Mon`o*ton"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of, pertaining to,
or uttered in, a monotone; monotonous.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Monotonical</xex> declamation.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chesterfield.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>Always increasing or always
decreasing, as the value of the independent variable increases; -- of a
function.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monotonist</ent>⟦br⟧
